ed: Migrated old business structure<br />\nFixed: store opening ours from admin end</p>\n<p>Version 1.5.9 (April 23, 2024)<br />\nAdded: Store set feature image when upload logo<br />\nAdded: Add description to membership oder details and order receipt page<br />\nUpdated:  Hide free ads if free ads off and membership is on</p>\n<p>Version 1.5.8 (Mar 15, 2024)<br />\nFixed: Edit membership edit issue<br />\nUpdate: membership menu UI</p>\n<p>Version 1.5.7 (Feb 22, 2024)<br />\nFixed: Pay per ad membership promotion issue</p>\n<p>Version 1.5.6 (Feb 20, 2023)<br />\nFixed: Store category display issue<br />\nFixed: Logo/banner update issue<br />\nAdded: Option for store review process<br />\nAdded: Badge for membership users<br />\nAdded: Badge for store owner<br />\nAdded: Store only for verified user [Seller Verification addon]</p>\n<p>Version 1.5.5 (Feb 05, 2023)<br />\nAdd: Form Builder Compatibility<br />\nFixed: Store RTL issue</p>\n<p>Version 1.5.3 (Nov 20, 2023)<br />\nFixed: My-account style issue</p>\n<p>Version 1.5.1 (Nov 08, 2023)<br />\nAdded: User Dashboard backward compatibility<br />\nVersion 1.5.0 (Nov 07, 2023)<br />\nAdded: New dashboard compatibility</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.33 (Sep 25, 2023)<br />\nFixed: Website link display issue<br />\nUpdated: Social Profile list<br />\nAdded:  Store rest api config<br />\nAdded: Category filter</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.32 (July 25, 2023)<br />\nUpdated: Membership api for APP</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.31 (July 25, 2023)<br />\nAdded: Add hook to remove nonce from contact form</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.30 (June 23, 2023)<br />\nAdded: Hook for carry forward expired membership data</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.29 (April 28, 2023)<br />\nAdded: PHP 8.2 compatibility<br />\nAdded: Login redirect to a single page for store contact</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.28 (Mar 09, 2023)<br />\nAdded: Pagination for Elementor Store addon<br />\nAdded: Settings for store pagination and grid column</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.27 (Mar 01, 2023)<br />\nFixed: Renew issue<br />\nFixed: Shortcode class load issue </p>\n<p>Version 1.4.26 (Feb 15, 2023)<br />\nAdded: Free ads count in dashboard statistics</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.25 (Jan 11, 2023)<br />\nFixed: Free and membership post count issue<br />\nAdded: New new new option for all users / Only membership</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.24 (Dec 06, 2022)<br />\nAdded: Listing renew from membership<br />\nVersion 1.4.23 (Nov 25, 2022)<br />\nFixed: Javascript issue with checkout<br />\nAdded: Added some hooks for the free version</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.21 (Sep 14, 2022)<br />\nAdded: Store review compatibility with Review Schema<br />\nFixed: Session error log</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.20 (Aug 12, 2022)<br />\nUpdated: Security &amp; Sanitisation<br />\nUpdate: Change text naming</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.19 (July 25, 2022)<br />\nFixed: Day start issue<br />\nAdded: Coupon addon compatibility</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.18 (July 06, 2022)<br />\nFixed: Week starts on from settings<br />\nFixed: Membership regular ad field issue</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.17 (Jul 01, 2022)<br />\nAdded: New Feature for Store Single Page builder.<br />\nVersion 1.4.14 (May 10, 2022)<br />\nFixed: PHP Warning issue</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.12 (April 12, 2022)<br />\nAdded: Store Grid/List Elementor Addon</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.10 (March 01, 2022)<br />\nFixed: Front-end dashboard store error<br />\nVersion 1.4.9 (Feb 16, 2022)<br />\nAdded: Store Category<br />\nVersion 1.4.8.2 (Dec 15, 2021)<br />\nFix : Auto redirect Membership checkout page<br />\nFix: Store contact form issue</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.8.1 (Dec 13, 2021)<br />\n Fixed: reCaptha issue for store contact form</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.8 (Dec 09, 2021)<br />\nAdd: Google Re-captcha V3 Support</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.7 (Nov 15, 2021)<br />\nFixed: Installing function not found issue</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.6.3 (Sep 28, 2021)<br />\nFixed: Review template loading issue<br />\nFixed: some coding issues<br />\nAdded: Addon filter to remove addon if installed</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.6.1 (Aug 13, 2021)<br />\nUpdate: Rest API<br />\nAdd: Control for Store contact info hide guest user. </p>\n<p>Version 1.4.5 (July 28, 2021)<br />\nFixed: Mobile app Rest Api call issue<br />\nImpromove: Classified listing free version dependency Update</p>\n<p>Version 1.4.4 (Jun 24, 2021)<br />\nFix: Radius Search<br />\nImprove: code to work Classified Pro version 2.0<br />\nVersion 1.4.2 (April 15, 2021)<br />\nAdd: Store api connect for app<br />\nVersion 1.4.0 (Mar 14, 2021)<br />\nAdd: Store Manager feature<br />\nVersion 1.3.28(Aug 11, 2020)<br />\nAdd: Promotion under Membership package<br />\nversion 1.3.22 (April 30, 2020)<br />\nAdd: Archive page<br />\nAdd: Store Category</p>\n<p>version 1.3.10 (Dec 11, 2019)<br />\nAdd: Social Icon<br />\nAdd: Store Rating<br />\nAdd: 24h Store hrs format</p>\n<p>version 1.1.80 (May 23, 2019)<br />\nAdd nofollow link in store url<br />\nVersion 1.1.6 (Apr 25, 2019)<br />\nAdd settings store only for membership</p>\n\";}s:13:\"license_check\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"msg\";s:33:\"No license key has been provided.\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:94:\"https://www.radiustheme.com/downloads/classified-listing-store-membership-addon-for-wordpress/\";s:7:\"package\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"icons\";s:228:\"a:2:{s:2:\"1x\";s:94:\"https://www.radiustheme.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2025/11/store-membership-addon-128x128.webp\";s:2:\"2x\";s:94:\"https://www.radiustheme.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2025/11/store-membership-addon-256x256.webp\";}\";s:7:\"banners\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:4:\"high\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"low\";s:0:\"\";}s:4:\"slug\";s:24:\"classified-listing-store\";s:3:\"url\";s:106:\"https://www.radiustheme.com/downloads/classified-listing-store-membership-addon-for-wordpress/?changelog=1\";s:12:\"last_updated\";s:19:\"2026-06-24 13:48:13\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;s:11548:\"<p>Classified Listing Store &amp; Membership addon				</p>\n<p>Create your store within in the Classified ads website so visitor can get all items easi